    <tasks>
        <task>
            <ID>1</ID>
            <parents>0</parents>
            <children>0</children>
            <time>300</time>
            <attentionRequired>true</attentionRequired>
            <taskString>Finely dice the bacon and onions and saute, but not brown.</taskString>
            <taskTitle>Bacon and onions</taskTitle>
        </task>
        <task>
            <ID>2</ID>
            <parents>0</parents>
            <children>0</children>
            <time>300</time>
            <attentionRequired>true</attentionRequired>
            <taskString>Roast minced meat as well as possible - finely divide.</taskString>
            <taskTitle>Roast minced meat.</taskTitle>
        </task>
        <task>
            <ID>3</ID>
            <parents>2</parents>
            <children>0</children>
            <time>150</time>
            <attentionRequired>true</attentionRequired>
            <taskString>Add all in a pot and add wine as well as the spices. </taskString>
            <taskTitle>Add everything to pot</taskTitle>
        </task>
        <task>
            <ID>4</ID>
            <parents>0</parents>
            <children>6</children>
            <time>500</time>
            <attentionRequired>false</attentionRequired>
            <taskString>Cook the pasta in 2-3 l salted water for about 10 minutes</taskString>
            <timerString>Pasta cooking.</timerString>
            <alertString>You're done cooking pasta.</alertString>
            <taskTitle>Done cooking.</taskTitle>
        </task>
        <task>
            <ID>5</ID>
            <parents>4</parents>
            <children>6</children>
            <time>3600</time>
            <attentionRequired>false</attentionRequired>
            <taskString>At least 1 h, better 2 h, simmer gently stirring occasionally. The sauce must be thick, but not firm.</taskString>
            <timerString>Sauce is simmering</timerString>
            <alertString>Your sauce is done.</alertString>
            <taskTitle>Simmer</taskTitle>
        </task>
        <task>
            <ID>6</ID>
            <parents>0</parents>
            <children>0</children>
            <time>60</time>
            <attentionRequired>true</attentionRequired>
            <taskString>Either serve separately or mix the sauce with the  pasta. Serve the parmesan.</taskString>
            <taskTitle>Serving the dish</taskTitle>
        </task>
    </tasks>
    <preparation></preparation>
    <variation>Add finely chopped peppers and carrots.</variation>
    <remark>
If no bacon is used, one should if possible use minced meat (half pork and half veal) or pure pork as the dish will be heartier and juicier.

</remark>
